Text.SourceString: Whoa! Hi there!... Oh, my starfish, you really startled me!//Ahem, anyway, it's nice to meet you. I'm <NPCName>Emeil</>, by the way.
Text.LocalizedString: Whoa! Hi there!... Oh, my starfish, you really startled me!//Ahem, anyway, it's nice to meet you. I'm <NPCName>Emeil</>, by the way.

Text.SourceString: Ah, you're still around, fantastic! This is going to be great, definitely great.//I mean, I think so, yeah.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, you're still around, fantastic! This is going to be great, definitely great.//I mean, I think so, yeah.

Text.SourceString: Um, I'll volunteer for the scouting mission! I mean, not that I'm the best swimmer, but I've read all about the currents, probably twice.
Text.LocalizedString: Um, I'll volunteer for the scouting mission! I mean, not that I'm the best swimmer, but I've read all about the currents, probably twice.

Text.SourceString: I've been thinking, maybe we should rearrange the armory? Not that there's anything wrong now, but, you know, just in case.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been thinking, maybe we should rearrange the armory? Not that there's anything wrong now, but, you know, just in case.

Text.SourceString: I'll go talk to <NPCName>Semeru</> and see what his take is on weapon rearrangement.
Text.LocalizedString: I'll go talk to <NPCName>Semeru</> and see what his take is on weapon rearrangement.

Text.SourceString: I've practiced this maneuver a hundred times last night.//<portrait=annoyed>Well, sort of practiced in my head, but still!
Text.LocalizedString: I've practiced this maneuver a hundred times last night.//<portrait=annoyed>Well, sort of practiced in my head, but still!

Text.SourceString: Do you think the fish ever find me odd? I mean, to them, I'm probably just a big, armored fish, right?
Text.LocalizedString: Do you think the fish ever find me odd? I mean, to them, I'm probably just a big, armored fish, right?

Text.SourceString: I was reading about sea currents and I had this thought...what if we're all just floating in a giant fishbowl? Makes me kind of anxious, thinking about it...//Maybe I should stop thinking about it. What do you think?
Text.LocalizedString: I was reading about sea currents and I had this thought...what if we're all just floating in a giant fishbowl? Makes me kind of anxious, thinking about it...//Maybe I should stop thinking about it. What do you think?

Text.SourceString: Me, on guard duty? I mean, if you need someone who's really good at jumping at shadows and getting startled by seaweed, then... yeah, I'm your merman. Ha ha...hmm...
Text.LocalizedString: Me, on guard duty? I mean, if you need someone who's really good at jumping at shadows and getting startled by seaweed, then... yeah, I'm your merman. Ha ha...hmm...

Text.SourceString: I'd probably lose a game of hide-and-seek with a clam. They're sneaky, you know, with their whole not-moving strategy.
Text.LocalizedString: I'd probably lose a game of hide-and-seek with a clam. They're sneaky, you know, with their whole not-moving strategy.

Text.SourceString: I tried to sharpen my trident and, well, it's actually a bit duller now.//I'm not sure how that happened. Reverse engineering skills, I guess?
Text.LocalizedString: I tried to sharpen my trident and, well, it's actually a bit duller now.//I'm not sure how that happened. Reverse engineering skills, I guess?

Text.SourceString: Did anyone else notice that the third coral from the left near the gate has a slightly more pinkish hue today? No? Just me then.
Text.LocalizedString: Did anyone else notice that the third coral from the left near the gate has a slightly more pinkish hue today? No? Just me then.

Text.SourceString: I've cataloged every type of sand grain in the kingdom. You never know when that sort of thing might come in handy.
Text.LocalizedString: I've cataloged every type of sand grain in the kingdom. You never know when that sort of thing might come in handy.

Text.SourceString: I couldn't help but observe that the algae on the east wall grows 0.03 cm faster per day.//It's fascinating, but also, does that mean something's off?
Text.LocalizedString: I couldn't help but observe that the algae on the east wall grows 0.03 cm faster per day.//It's fascinating, but also, does that mean something's off?

Text.SourceString: Sorry for apologizing so much. I just really want to make sure I'm doing everything right for the squad, you know?//<portrait=annoyed>Argh, and there I go apologizing once more!
Text.LocalizedString: Sorry for apologizing so much. I just really want to make sure I'm doing everything right for the squad, you know?//<portrait=annoyed>Argh, and there I go apologizing once more!

Text.SourceString: I'll always be here for you! Sorry, that probably came out more melodramatic than I thought. What I mean is, I'm always here, um, for security support!
Text.LocalizedString: I'll always be here for you! Sorry, that probably came out more melodramatic than I thought. What I mean is, I'm always here, um, for security support!

Text.SourceString: Was that a giant squid? No? Just a shadow, right. Sorry, false alarm!//<portrait=normal>My nerves got the better of me, let's just keep swimming.
Text.LocalizedString: Was that a giant squid? No? Just a shadow, right. Sorry, false alarm!//<portrait=normal>My nerves got the better of me, let's just keep swimming.

Text.SourceString: The training exercise today, well...that's great! Well, sort of great – it's exciting but also a bit, um, nerve-wracking.
Text.LocalizedString: The training exercise today, well...that's great! Well, sort of great – it's exciting but also a bit, um, nerve-wracking.

Text.SourceString: I found an injured shrimp and I just had to help it. It's not the usual soldier thing to do, I guess, but leaving it there didn't feel right.//Where's my cookie? Ha ha...kidding...um...
Text.LocalizedString: I found an injured shrimp and I just had to help it. It's not the usual soldier thing to do, I guess, but leaving it there didn't feel right.//Where's my cookie? Ha ha...kidding...um...

Text.SourceString: If anyone's feeling down, just come talk to me. I'm not sure how good my advice is, but I'm here to listen, always.
Text.LocalizedString: If anyone's feeling down, just come talk to me. I'm not sure how good my advice is, but I'm here to listen, always.

Text.SourceString: I made some extra seaweed wraps, in case anyone forgot lunch. They're nothing fancy, but I made them fresh – I hope they're at least okay.
Text.LocalizedString: I made some extra seaweed wraps, in case anyone forgot lunch. They're nothing fancy, but I made them fresh – I hope they're at least okay.

Text.SourceString: Every time it starts raining up there, I get this funny feeling. Like, what if it never stops? That's silly, right? Right?
Text.LocalizedString: Every time it starts raining up there, I get this funny feeling. Like, what if it never stops? That's silly, right? Right?

Text.SourceString: Every time it starts raining up there, I get this funny feeling. Like, what if it never stops? That's silly, right? Right?
Text.LocalizedString: Every time it starts raining up there, I get this funny feeling. Like, what if it never stops? That's silly, right? Right?

Text.SourceString: Oh, rain again... I mean, it's good for the sea and all, but it makes everything so murky and, uh, unpredictable.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, rain again... I mean, it's good for the sea and all, but it makes everything so murky and, uh, unpredictable.

Text.SourceString: Oh, rain again... I mean, it's good for the sea and all, but it makes everything so murky and, uh, unpredictable.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, rain again... I mean, it's good for the sea and all, but it makes everything so murky and, uh, unpredictable.

Text.SourceString: Do you think rain is confusing for fish? Or is that just me overthinking? I mean, water falling into more water... it's a bit odd, isn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: Do you think rain is confusing for fish? Or is that just me overthinking? I mean, water falling into more water... it's a bit odd, isn't it?

Text.SourceString: Do you think rain is confusing for fish? Or is that just me overthinking? I mean, water falling into more water... it's a bit odd, isn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: Do you think rain is confusing for fish? Or is that just me overthinking? I mean, water falling into more water... it's a bit odd, isn't it?

Text.SourceString: Today is so cold! I always worry if I'm swimming too slowly. Hypothermia is a real thing, you know?
Text.LocalizedString: Today is so cold! I always worry if I'm swimming too slowly. Hypothermia is a real thing, you know?

Text.SourceString: *Brrr*
Text.LocalizedString: *Brrr*

Text.SourceString: I'm freezing over here!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm freezing over here!

Text.SourceString: I'm so good at overthinking, I bet if there was a thought marathon, I'd run it in record time – with extra loops. Ha ha ha! Hmm...
Text.LocalizedString: I'm so good at overthinking, I bet if there was a thought marathon, I'd run it in record time – with extra loops. Ha ha ha! Hmm...

Text.SourceString: No, I really should cut that out. My therapist says I need to quit poking fun at myself and start practicing some of that 'love yourself' stuff.
Text.LocalizedString: No, I really should cut that out. My therapist says I need to quit poking fun at myself and start practicing some of that 'love yourself' stuff.

Text.SourceString: Do you ever think about whether fish get thirsty? I mean, the regular fish, not merfolk like us...//I know, I know, it's a silly thought, but it just swims around in my head sometimes.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you ever think about whether fish get thirsty? I mean, the regular fish, not merfolk like us...//I know, I know, it's a silly thought, but it just swims around in my head sometimes.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I wonder if seaweed ever feels self-conscious about how it floats so awkwardly.//Probably not... But if I were seaweed, I definitely would be!
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I wonder if seaweed ever feels self-conscious about how it floats so awkwardly.//Probably not... But if I were seaweed, I definitely would be!

Text.SourceString: I sometimes lie awake, worrying about sea storms. Not that I can do anything about them, but what if they sneak up on us?
Text.LocalizedString: I sometimes lie awake, worrying about sea storms. Not that I can do anything about them, but what if they sneak up on us?

Text.SourceString: My therapist advised me to take deep breaths when I'm overthinking. So, if you see me taking long, dramatic pauses, that's probably why.
Text.LocalizedString: My therapist advised me to take deep breaths when I'm overthinking. So, if you see me taking long, dramatic pauses, that's probably why.

Text.SourceString: In therapy, we're focusing on building confidence. Like, 'Believe in yourself, <NPCName>Emeil</>!' Easier said than done, but I'm giving it a try.
Text.LocalizedString: In therapy, we're focusing on building confidence. Like, 'Believe in yourself, <NPCName>Emeil</>!' Easier said than done, but I'm giving it a try.

Text.SourceString: I have to remember what my therapist said about not always apologizing for everything.//It's tough, but apparently, it's important for self-esteem or something.
Text.LocalizedString: I have to remember what my therapist said about not always apologizing for everything.//It's tough, but apparently, it's important for self-esteem or something.

Text.SourceString: In one of my therapy sessions, we did this exercise where I compliment myself.//I said, 'Nice fins, <NPCName>Emeil</>.' Felt weird, but great at the same time.
Text.LocalizedString: In one of my therapy sessions, we did this exercise where I compliment myself.//I said, 'Nice fins, <NPCName>Emeil</>.' Felt weird, but great at the same time.

Text.SourceString: I did a breathing exercise this one time, and I got so relaxed I almost floated away. My therapist had to reel me back in – literally!
Text.LocalizedString: I did a breathing exercise this one time, and I got so relaxed I almost floated away. My therapist had to reel me back in – literally!

Text.SourceString: My therapist asked me to keep a worry diary. Felt weird at first, but hey, it actually helps.//I carry my scroll everywhere now. So watch out, if you annoy me, you're going straight into my worry diary!
Text.LocalizedString: My therapist asked me to keep a worry diary. Felt weird at first, but hey, it actually helps.//I carry my scroll everywhere now. So watch out, if you annoy me, you're going straight into my worry diary!
